-- Kuwait Plans `Some Increase' in Spending Next Fiscal Year, Al-Shimali Says
-- B y   F i o n a   M a c D o n a l d   a n d   D a h l i a   K h o l a i f
-- 2010-11-06T10:06:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-06/kuwait-plans-some-increase-in-spending-next-fiscal-year-al-shimali-says.html
Kuwait plans “some increase” in
government spending in the fiscal year starting April 1, Finance
Minister Mustafa al-Shimali told reporters today in Kuwait City,
where he is attending a summit of Gulf Cooperation Council
finance ministers.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Fiona MacDonald in Kuwait at 
